ympics are fast approaching, and South Africa is poised to make a splash with a talented group of athletes across multiple sports.\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 429, \"end\": 441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999994579412, \"rank\": 5.420176106656668e-10, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From track and field to swimming and surfing, here are five South African athletes to keep an eye on as they chase Olympic glory in the City of Light.\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 677, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wayde van Niekerk, the current world record holder in the 400m, will be looking to reclaim his Olympic crown in Paris.\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 679, \"end\": 696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wayde van Niekerk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\"}, {\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9278896936620858e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old missed out on the podium in Tokyo but has been rounding back into form.\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 842, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.5440470869362777, \"rank\": 0.8380746437806653, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Expect van Niekerk to be a major medal threat in the 400m and 4x400m relay for South Africa at the 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999994579412, \"rank\": 5.420176106656668e-10, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After bursting onto the scene with gold and silver medals in Tokyo, swimmer Tatjana Schoenmaker has established herself as one of the top breaststrokers in the world.\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1063, \"end\": 1068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.5440470869362777, \"rank\": 0.8380746437806653, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tatjana_Schoenmaker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tatjana Schoenmaker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tatjana_Schoenmaker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tatjana_Schoenmaker\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still only 26, Schoenmaker will be in her prime in 2024 and aiming to add to her Olympic hardware.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa's swimming sensation is a must-watch in Paris.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1269, \"end\": 1281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999994579412, \"rank\": 5.420176106656668e-10, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\